
Overview of noun suggestion

The noun suggestion has 6 senses (first 4 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (13) suggestion -- (an idea that is suggested; "the picnic was her suggestion")
2. (9) suggestion, proposition, proffer -- (a proposal offered for acceptance or rejection; "it was a suggestion we couldn't refuse")
3. (1) trace, hint, suggestion -- (a just detectable amount; "he speaks French with a trace of an accent")
4. (1) suggestion, prompting -- (persuasion formulated as a suggestion)
5. suggestion -- (the sequential mental process in which one thought leads to another by association)
6. hypnotism, mesmerism, suggestion -- (the act of inducing hypnosis)
